UNITED STATES of America, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Mitchel D. COHEN, dba the White House, Defendant-Appellant. No. 6-4. Temporary Emergency Court of Appeals. May 28, 1974.

Before TAMM, Chief Judge, and CHRISTENSEN and JOHNSON, Judges.

ORDER OF AFFIRMANCE UNDER RULE 28

TAMM, Chief Judge.

The court having considered the record and briefs on this appeal and having found no reversible error in the decision of the District Court, 380 F.Supp. 147, the judgment is affirmed.
